<br>
My husband did experience a physical death. I will not get into much detail for it was his experience. He did leave his body, enter the tunnel and see the light. He is not afraid of death. He knows the soul lives on through his own experience.<br>
<br>
One thing I know for sure is that this life is the only life you will be exactly who you are right now. <br>
<br>
 <br>
